	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Golden Rule</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Don't modify temporary variables in your NMI.
<br />
<br />Just don't.
<br />
<br />Failure to observe this rule can lead to many, many wasted hours trying to track down a really, really tricky bug.
<br />
<br /><img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


